The petition comes after Lilly Wachowski, the co-director of blockbuster films such as the The Matrix and V For Vendetta, was doorstepped by a journalist from The Daily Mail last week.  The journalist threatened Lilly saying if she didn=E2=80=99t do an interview with the paper, she would be immediately outed.

