=E2=80=9CEnough is enough. The Daily Mail must stop outing trans people. It=E2=80=99s not news, and it=E2=80=99s not acceptable,=E2=80=9D added Thomas.

After the death of Lucy Meadows, 200,000 SumOfUs members signed a petition asking The Daily Mail to sack Richard Littlejohn.

